msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Ukuba ungaphandle kwe-US, sicebisa i-NOWPayments (imali eziphantsi, ngqo "
"kwi-wallet yakho). Ukuba ungaphakathi kwe-US, i-Stripe Crypto nayo ingenye "
"enye eoption. Ungavumela iinkonzo ezininzi kwaye uvumele iindwendwe zakho "
"ukukhetha!"

