"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"I-widget enamandla, yamahhala yokunikezela nokuhlawula evumela uvakasheli "
"wakho ukukuxhasa nge-ikhdhoni okanye imali ye-ikhrypto (Quai). Akukho imali "
"yenyanga, akukho ukubhaliswa kwabanye – ukuze ufumane kuphela i-wallet yakho"
" kunye neenkonzo zamahhala."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Ezinye i-browsers zivali script zothathu ngenxa yokhuseleko. Le proxy "
"ithumela script ngasengaba kwiseva yakho ukuze igqibe lezi zivali."

