"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"Ungabuyisela i-URLs ze-script ezilandelayo ukuba i-URLs zangaphambili "
"zishintshe okanye ukuba ufuna ukusebenzisa i-CDN eyongezelelweyo."

